show.title: Operation Ex-Lover
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/BuKm5k
show.description: Six years ago, Mansi chose to break up with her boyfriend Rahul to avoid hindering his promising military career due to her overwhelming debt. Six years later, they reunite in a different city, Rahul is now a commanding officer, while Mansi is a single mother. Their chemistry reignites, but their bonding faces uncertainties of their class differences and pressure from people around them. This time, will they find their way back to love again?
